-- ZTE to Sell Mobile Phones Under Own Name, Handelsblatt Says
-- B y   K o n s t a n t i n   R i f f l e r
-- 2012-02-20T07:48:16Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-02-20/zte-to-sell-mobile-phones-under-own-name-handelsblatt-says.html
ZTE Corp. (000063) , a Chinese mobile phone
producer and mobile communication system provider, is going to
sell mobile phones under its own name on the German market,
 Handelsblatt  reported.  “We want to become a renowned brand here,”  John Lee , head
ZTE’s German operations, according to Handelsblatt. Until
recently, the company sold mobile phones under the brand of
various network providers, Handelsblatt said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Konstantin Riffler in Frankfurt at 
 kriffler@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Angela Cullen at 
 acullen8@bloomberg.net  